" Switching Tabs
nnoremap ˙ gT
nnoremap <M-H> gT
nnoremap ¬ gt
nnoremap <M-L> gt

" Opening an emptry new tab
nnoremap ˜ :tabnew<CR>
nnoremap <M-N> :tabnew<CR>

" Opening current file in a new tab
nnoremap † :tabedit %<CR>
nnoremap <M-T> :tabedit %<CR>

" Switching Windows
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

" Open Nerd Tree * Need to Install nerdtree
nnoremap <C-n> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>

" Deleting using backspace
nnoremap <BS> X
